[
  {
    "text": "Hi, I am Lawrence from the NFC team. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=1"
  },
  {
    "text": "Welcome to this Core NFC update. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=4"
  },
  {
    "text": "We have got a new feature for Core NFC this year ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=7"
  },
  {
    "text": "that will not only enhance the NFC experience, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=11"
  },
  {
    "text": "but also greatly simplify the process of handling NFC tags ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=14"
  },
  {
    "text": "within your applications. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=18"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you are new to Core NFC, I recommend that you watch ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=20"
  },
  {
    "text": "the \"Introduction to Core NFC\" video released last year. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=23"
  },
  {
    "text": "With the new background tag reading feature, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=28"
  },
  {
    "text": "the iPhone is able to automatically read NFC tags ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=30"
  },
  {
    "text": "and deliver them to the appropriate apps. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=32"
  },
  {
    "text": "The mechanism is able to perform ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=36"
  },
  {
    "text": "the necessary app launch or bringing the application ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=38"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the foreground state. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=41"
  },
  {
    "text": "We are excited to see ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=43"
  },
  {
    "text": "how this can make the user experience even better ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=44"
  },
  {
    "text": "and make it easier for apps to handle NFC tags.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=47"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this video, I will discuss the NFC tag data requirements, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=52"
  },
  {
    "text": "the expected user experience, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=56"
  },
  {
    "text": "when background tag reading is supported, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=58"
  },
  {
    "text": "and some example code snippets to get you started. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=60"
  },
  {
    "text": "Background tag reading ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=64"
  },
  {
    "text": "will work with any NDEF formatted tag ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=65"
  },
  {
    "text": "whose NDEF message includes a URL record. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=68"
  },
  {
    "text": "Only the first discovered URL record in the NDEF message ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=71"
  },
  {
    "text": "will be processed. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=75"
  },
  {
    "text": "The URL record must contain a valid Apple Universal Link URL ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=77"
  },
  {
    "text": "in order for the message to be routed to an application. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=81"
  },
  {
    "text": "iOS will route the message to the application ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=85"
  },
  {
    "text": "registered with the Apple Universal Link. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=87"
  },
  {
    "text": "While the screen is on, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=91"
  },
  {
    "text": "background tag reading will scan for nearby NFC tags. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=92"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once a compatible tag is successfully read, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=96"
  },
  {
    "text": "a pop-up from the Notification Center ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=99"
  },
  {
    "text": "will appear on the iPhone screen. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=101"
  },
  {
    "text": "Tapping on the notification will trigger the delivery ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=103"
  },
  {
    "text": "of a NSUserActivity object to the associated application ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=106"
  },
  {
    "text": "using the Apple Universal Link mechanisms. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=110"
  },
  {
    "text": "By default, Safari will handle ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=113"
  },
  {
    "text": "all unregistered application links ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=115"
  },
  {
    "text": "and it will only process the URL payload. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=118"
  },
  {
    "text": "There are also other URL schemes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=121"
  },
  {
    "text": "that trigger a default iOS behavior, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=124"
  },
  {
    "text": "which I will discuss later on. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=126"
  },
  {
    "text": "Any unprocessed notification will be saved ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=129"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the Notification Center for future reference. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=131"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here is what happens when the user taps an NFC tag. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=135"
  },
  {
    "text": "A notification will be shown, and tapping on the notification ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=139"
  },
  {
    "text": "will launch the registered application. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=142"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once the application is running, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=144"
  },
  {
    "text": "tapping on the NFC tag again will trigger a new notification. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=146"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=150"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=154"
  },
  {
    "text": "When a tag is read in the locked state, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=162"
  },
  {
    "text": "the user will be prompted to first unlock the phone ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=165"
  },
  {
    "text": "before the tag data can be processed. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=167"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=170"
  },
  {
    "text": "Background tag reading is supported on iPhone XS, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=180"
  },
  {
    "text": "iPhone XS Max, and iPhone XR. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=183"
  },
  {
    "text": "The phone must first be unlocked at least once after boot up ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=187"
  },
  {
    "text": "for background tag reading to be operational. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=190"
  },
  {
    "text": "After first unlock, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=193"
  },
  {
    "text": "the device will scan for NFC tags in the background ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=194"
  },
  {
    "text": "whenever the display is on regardless of the lock state, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=197"
  },
  {
    "text": "except for the following conditions: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=200"
  },
  {
    "text": "a Core NFC reader session is in progress, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=203"
  },
  {
    "text": "Wallet or Apple Pay are in use, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=206"
  },
  {
    "text": "cameras are in use, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=209"
  },
  {
    "text": "or the device is in Airplane Mode. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=211"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now let us walk through the required implementation steps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=214"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your application ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=217"
  },
  {
    "text": "to receive the content of the NFC tag. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=218"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is broken down into three main steps. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=221"
  },
  {
    "text": "You will need to register the associated domains ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=224"
  },
  {
    "text": "for your application as per the Universal Link requirements. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=227"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then you will need to adopt the UIApplicationDelegate protocol, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=231"
  },
  {
    "text": "application(_:continue: restorationHandler:) function. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=235"
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, you will need to extract the NDEF message ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=240"
  },
  {
    "text": "from the ndefMessagePayload property ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=243"
  },
  {
    "text": "of the NSUserActivity object. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=246"
  },
  {
    "text": "To register your domain in your app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=250"
  },
  {
    "text": "open your project in Xcode and enter the server host domain ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=252"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the Associated Domains section. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=255"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here is a code snippet ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=259"
  },
  {
    "text": "illustrating how to receive a NSUserActivity object ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=261"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your UIKit application. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=264"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, import the Core NFC framework. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=267"
  },
  {
    "text": "Implement the UIApplicationDelegate ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=270"
  },
  {
    "text": "protocol method, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=272"
  },
  {
    "text": "application (_:continue: restorationHandler:). ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=273"
  },
  {
    "text": "Validate the activity type is NSUserActivityTypeBrowsingWeb ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=278"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the handler.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=283"
  },
  {
    "text": "Read the NFCNDEFMessage ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=287"
  },
  {
    "text": "from the ndefMessagePayload property. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=290"
  },
  {
    "text": "This contains the entire NDEF message ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=293"
  },
  {
    "text": "read from the NFC tag. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=295"
  },
  {
    "text": "The message contains an array of NFC NDEF payload records. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=298"
  },
  {
    "text": "Each NDEF record contains the typeNameFormat, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=303"
  },
  {
    "text": "the Type, the Identifier, and the data payload. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=307"
  },
  {
    "text": "One of the NFC NDEF payload ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=311"
  },
  {
    "text": "will contain the URL record with the Universal Link ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=314"
  },
  {
    "text": "that triggered the launch of your application. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=317"
  },
  {
    "text": "Please refer to the NFC Forum specifications ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=320"
  },
  {
    "text": "regarding the various record type definitions. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=322"
  },
  {
    "text": "If the received NSUserActivity object ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=326"
  },
  {
    "text": "did not originate from the background tag reading, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=329"
  },
  {
    "text": "then the resulting NFCNDEFMessage ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=331"
  },
  {
    "text": "will contain exactly one NFC NDEF payload object ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=334"
  },
  {
    "text": "with its typeNameFormat property set to NFCTypeNameFormatEmpty.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=338"
  },
  {
    "text": "If the URL record does not contain a Universal Link, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=346"
  },
  {
    "text": "iOS can still handle many of the same URI schemes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=350"
  },
  {
    "text": "as the QR code scanner such as HomeKit, SMS, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=353"
  },
  {
    "text": "GPS, and others. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=357"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here is an example ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=359"
  },
  {
    "text": "of some of the various supported schemes. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=360"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can find more information about Core NFC ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=364"
  },
  {
    "text": "on developer.apple.com.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-702/?time=366"
  }
]